item.title: Selected Undergraduate Projects
item.description: Reducing effects of joints clearance on the behavior of the parallel manipulators(A Part of Bachelor Thesis) 2013 â€“ 2015 I passed my bachelor thesis under the supervision of Prof.Daniali about the dynamic analysis of the mechanical system. As a part of my bachelor thesis, with collaboration with Dr.Varedi, we analyzed the effect of clearance Joints on the performance of the parallel robot. Clearance imposes some uncontrollable degrees of freedom to a manipulator.
